title: Priyanka Chopra looks red hot in new 'Baywatch' poster!
text:
Priyanka Chopra in 'Baywatch' 
Bollywood actress Priyanka Chopra, who will be making her Hollywood debut with 'Baywatch', has shared a new poster introducing her character Victoria Leeds in the film.
Here's the new poster: 
Being bad can be so good. Coming soon.. #VictoriaLeeds #Baywatch #may26th pic.twitter.com/rNRsHRtnQm 
â€” PRIYANKA (@priyankachopra) February 22, 2017 Doesn't she look smokin' hot?
'Baywatch' also stars Dwayne 'The Rock' Johnson and Zac Efron. 
Fondly called as 'Desi girl', thanks to the hit number from 'Dostana', Priyanka has given critically acclaimed performances in movies like 'Fashion', 'Kaminey', 'Agneepath', 'Barfi!', 'Mary Kom' and 'Bajirao Mastani'.
The National Award-winning actress, also a former beauty queen, has also impressed many with her act in 'Quantico'. She is currently seen in the second season of the show.
Directed by Seth Gordon, the film also features Alexandra Daddario, Kelly Rohrbach and Ilfenesh Hadera.
